#: ../../misc.md:1
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "杂项"

#: ../../misc.md:3
msgid "Types"
msgstr "类型"

#: ../../misc.md:5
msgid "Introspection"
msgstr "反射"

#: ../../misc.md:7
msgid ""
"*New in Koffi 2.0: `koffi.resolve()`, new in Koffi 2.2: "
"`koffi.offsetof()`*"
msgstr ""
"*引入自Koffi 2.0: `koffi.resolve()`, 引入自Koffi 2.2: `koffi.offsetof()`*"

#: ../../misc.md:10
msgid ""
"The value returned by `introspect()` has **changed in version 2.0 and in "
"version 2.2**."
msgstr ""
"`introspect()`返回的值在**版本2.0和2.2变更了**"

#: ../../misc.md:12
msgid ""
"In Koffi 1.x, it could only be used with struct types and returned the "
"object passed to koffi.struct() with the member names and types."
msgstr ""
"在Koffi 1.x中, 它只能被用于结构体类型且返回传入`koffi.struct()`的含有成员名称和类型的对象."

#: ../../misc.md:14
msgid ""
"Starting in Koffi 2.2, each record member is exposed as an object "
"containing the name, the type and the offset within the record."
msgstr ""
"自从Koffi 2.2起, 结构中的每个成员都有一个含有名称, 类型以及偏移的对象."

#: ../../misc.md:16
msgid "Consult the [migration guide](migration.md) for more information."
msgstr "查看[迁移指南](migration.md)来获取更多信息."

#: ../../misc.md:19
msgid ""
"Use `koffi.introspect(type)` to get detailed information about a type: "
"name, primitive, size, alignment, members (record types), reference type "
"(array, pointer) and length (array)."
msgstr ""
"使用`koffi.introspect(type)`来获取一个类型的细节信息: "
"名称, 原始类型, 大小, 对齐, 成员(结构), 引用类型(数组, 指针)和长度(数组)."

#: ../../misc.md:44
msgid ""
"Koffi also exposes a few more utility functions to get a subset of this "
"information:"
msgstr ""
"Koffi也额外提供了一些实用函数来获取这些信息的一个子集:"

#: ../../misc.md:46
msgid "`koffi.sizeof(type)` to get the size of a type"
msgstr "使用`koffi.sizeof(type)`来获取类型的大小"

#: ../../misc.md:47
msgid "`koffi.alignof(type)` to get the alignment of a type"
msgstr "使用`koffi.alignof(type)`来获取类型的对齐"

#: ../../misc.md:48
msgid "`koffi.offsetof(type, member_name)` to get the offset of a record member"
msgstr "使用`koffi.offsetof(type, member_name)`来获取结构成员的偏移"

#: ../../misc.md:49
msgid "`koffi.resolve(type)` to get the resolved type object from a type string"
msgstr "使用`koffi.resolve(type)`来从一个类型字符串解析出类型对象."

#: ../../misc.md:51
msgid ""
"Just like before, you can refer to primitive types by their name or "
"through `koffi.types`:"
msgstr ""
"就像以往一样, 你可以通过名称或`koffi.types`来引用原生类型."

#: ../../misc.md:59
msgid "Aliases"
msgstr "别名"

#: ../../misc.md:61
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.0*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.0引入*"

#: ../../misc.md:63
msgid ""
"You can alias a type with `koffi.alias(name, type)`. Aliased types are "
"completely equivalent."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用`koffi.alias(name, type)`来为一个类型创建别名. 别名类型和目标类型完全一样."

#: ../../misc.md:65
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "设置"

#: ../../misc.md:67
msgid "Memory usage"
msgstr "内存使用情况"

#: ../../misc.md:69
msgid "For synchronous/normal calls, Koffi uses two preallocated memory blocks:"
msgstr "对于同步/普通调用, Koffi使用两块预分配的内存块:"

#: ../../misc.md:71
msgid ""
"One to construct the C stack and assign registers, subsequently used by "
"the platform-specific assembly code (1 MiB by default)"
msgstr ""
"一个用于构造C堆栈和为寄存器赋值, 最终被平台汇编使用(默认1MiB)"

#: ../../misc.md:72
msgid "One to allocate strings and big objects/structs (2 MiB by default)"
msgstr "一个用于分配字符串和大对象/结构体(默认2MiB)"

#: ../../misc.md:74
msgid ""
"Unless very big strings or objects (at least more than one page of "
"memory) are used, Koffi does not directly allocate any extra memory "
"during calls or callbacks. However, please note that the JS engine (V8) "
"might."
msgstr ""
"除非使用了非常大的字符串或对象(至少超过一页大), Koffi不会在调用或回调时直接分配任何额外的内存. "
"然而, 请注意JS引擎(V8)可能会."

#: ../../misc.md:76
msgid ""
"The size (in bytes) of these preallocated blocks can be changed. Use "
"`koffi.config()` to get an object with the settings, and "
"`koffi.config(obj)` to apply new settings."
msgstr ""
"可以更改这些预分配块的大小(字节). 使用`koffi.config()`来获取包含这些设置的对象, 然后使用`koffi.config(obj)`来应用新设置."

#: ../../misc.md:83
msgid ""
"The same is true for asynchronous calls. When an asynchronous call is "
"made, Koffi will allocate new blocks unless there is an unused (resident)"
" set of blocks still available. Once the asynchronous call is finished, "
"these blocks are freed if there are more than `resident_async_pools` sets"
" of blocks left around."
msgstr ""
"对于异步调用来说也是一样的. 当异步调用发起后, 除非有未使用(驻留)的块可用, Koffi会分配新的块. "
"一旦异步调用完成, 超过`resident_async_pools`数量的块会被释放."

#: ../../misc.md:85
msgid "There cannot be more than `max_async_calls` running at the same time."
msgstr "异步调用同时只能执行`max_async_calls`个."

#: ../../misc.md:87
msgid "Default settings"
msgstr "默认设置"

